      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Query Validity Check\nThe AI Agent first checks whether the incoming query is valid \nor gibberish.\n\n- If gibberish → log it to the Google Sheet and stop (no \n  further processing).\n- If valid → continue to the next step (AI Agent response \n  + routing).",
